problem_data.title: Palindrome Partitioning II
problem_data.description: Given a string s, partition s such that every substring of the partition is a palindrome. Return the minimum cuts needed for a palindrome partitioning of s.

examples.explanation: The palindrome partitioning ["aa","b"] could be produced using 1 cut.
